show page virtual view, FvwmPager
make sure you set the module path in .fvwm2rc

ModulePath /usr/lib/fvwm/2.6.9/

AddToFunc StartFunction
+ I Module      FvwmPager *

Style FvwmPager    NoTitle,  Sticky, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkipIcon, CirculateSkip                                                                                                     
